edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database

Class DataDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.ansci.flip.database.DataDB

  • public class DataDB
extends java.lang.Object
    Auxiliary object that is used mainly to keep the basic profile of a selected population, but it can be used for other purposes.
    Profile consists of Object's identifier, name, date of creation, comments, associated course and the object itself.
    Author:
    patricio
